The boxing fraternity and the country at large are mourning the tragic death of Simiso Buthelezi. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The boxing fraternity and the country at large are mourning the tragic death of Simiso Buthelezi. READ: SA boxer dies from brain injury The boxer collapsed during his WBF All Africa Lightweight bout against Siphesihle Mntungwa on Sunday. He died after suffering bleeding on the brain and being placed in an induced coma. 